Maybe not that specific, but
I can pick the kind of people I want, and

7
00:00:25.249 --> 00:00:29.542
I just take those gaps,
those things that I don't feel I know,

8
00:00:29.542 --> 00:00:34.424
turn them into questions, shove that out,
and get people to respond.

9
