If I don't have the money to do that,
I mean, normally,

11
00:00:41.111 --> 00:00:43.700
I like to send out survey
to like 130 people,

12
00:00:43.700 --> 00:00:48.384
seems to be a number I've randomly settled
on because it's a reasonably big number.

13
00:00:48.384 --> 00:00:51.618
But, of course,
when you go into that number of people and

14
00:00:51.618 --> 00:00:55.651
if I have a lot of questions,
that could be costing me $300, right?

15
00:00:55.651 --> 00:00:57.670
Which I don't always have, right?

